                </names>
                <summary>The laying of the corner stone of the new Methodist Church has been
                    postponed due to bad weather until September 27. Article includes a schedule of
                    the procession and the names of speakers who will give addresses.</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>6</column>
                <head>Typhoid Fever</head>
                <origin>Tenth Legion</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>There has been a lot of sickness in the Valley near Edinburg and in Page
                    due to typhoid fever.</summary>
            </div>
